Modul org.freedesktop.dbus
Package org.freedesktop.dbus.annotations

Annotationsschnittstelle DBusProperties

@Target(TYPE) @Retention(RUNTIME) public @interface DBusProperties
Container for the multiple DBusProperty annotations in the single class. You probably don't want to use this annotation in your code, please use DBusProperty.
